import React from 'react'
import "`./styles.css`"

const DrawCards = ({ user }) => {

    const { name, edad, isAlive, profile } = user

    return ( <
        div >
        <
        h1 > { name } < /h1> <
        h3 > The age from user is: { edad } < /h3> <
        h2 > this person is: { isAlive } < /h2> <
        p > { profile } < /p> < /
        div >
    )
}

export default DrawCards
